OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F427A1774523167
OL,3,CEasyJet boss warns fliers to book
OL,4,Cearly amid fuel price spikes
OL,6,FThe boss of airline easyJet has warned
OL,7,Fholidaymakers to book early as
OL,8,Faviation fuel costs spike because of
OL,9,Fthe ongoing war in Iran.
OL,11,FKenton Jarvis said the budget flyer
OL,12,Fwas "well-hedged" as it had fuel
OL,13,Fsupplies secured in advance but the
OL,14,Fpricing currently was "volatile" since
OL,15,Fthis "terrible war started".
OL,17,FHe was speaking at Newcastle Airport,
OL,18,Fwhere easyJet announced it was opening
OL,19,Fa new base with three aircraft,
OL,20,Foperating 86 flights per week on 22
OL,21,Froutes from the hub.
OL,26,@tD@EOUtD@QO]vD@WOUvD@`O]wD@FOUwD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/7
