CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F427A1774523167
OL,3,CEasyJet boss warns fliers to book
OL,4,Cearly amid fuel price spikes
OL,6,FThe plan should support 1,200 UK jobs
OL,7,Fincluding 140 posts for pilots and
OL,8,Fcabin crew.
OL,10,FMr Jarvis, who arrived in Newcastle on
OL,11,Fa specially-arranged flight from
OL,12,FLuton, said UK growth from regional
OL,13,Fairports was up by more than 30% in
OL,14,Fthe past three years.
OL,16,FAsked if this was the right time to
OL,17,Fexpand, given the ongoing crisis in
OL,18,Fthe Gulf, he told the Press
OL,19,FAssociation: "We take very much long
OL,20,Fterm views when we do this.
OL,26,@{D@NOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/7
