OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,428,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F427A1774523167
OL,3,CEasyJet boss warns fliers to book
OL,4,Cearly amid fuel price spikes
OL,6,F"This is something we're doing for the
OL,7,Fmedium term."
OL,9,FOn increased fuel prices, he said:
OL,10,F"One thing we have seen is fuel is
OL,11,Fvery volatile over the last few weeks
OL,12,Fsince this terrible war started, and
OL,13,Fwe're seeing it completely elevated at
OL,14,Fthe moment.
OL,16,F"As an airline, easyJet is very well-
OL,17,Fhedged, so we buy our fuel in advance,
OL,18,Fwhich means we've got fuel at
OL,19,Fattractive prices for the coming
OL,20,Fmonths.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@MO]rD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,428,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F427A1774523167
OL,3,CEasyJet boss warns fliers to book
OL,4,Cearly amid fuel price spikes
OL,6,F"But over time (...) yes, I expect if
OL,7,Ffuel remains at this level, the prices
OL,8,Fwill become elevated.
OL,10,F"Fuel prices will have to go up in
OL,11,Fwhich case, I just recommend booking
OL,12,Fas early as possible."
OL,14,FMr Jarvis said airlines like easyJet
OL,15,Fworked on "thin" margins of #6 to #7
OL,16,Fper seat, so there was a need to
OL,17,Foffset increased costs with
OL,18,Fefficiencies, but that would be
OL,19,Fdifficult.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUtD@VO]wD@KOUwD@PO]
