PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F427A1774523167
OL,3,CEasyJet boss warns fliers to book
OL,4,Cearly amid fuel price spikes
OL,6,FThe operator has noted increased
OL,7,Fdemand for destinations away from the
OL,8,Fconflict, including the Canaries,
OL,9,FSpain, Portugal, Malta and Greece,
OL,10,Fwith "softening demand" for Turkey and
OL,11,FCyprus.
OL,13,FBut demand for holidays in general was
OL,14,Fholding up, he said, despite fears
OL,15,Fover the cost of living in the UK.
OL,26,@rD@FOUrD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/7
