FL,428,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F427A1774523167
OL,3,CEasyJet boss warns fliers to book
OL,4,Cearly amid fuel price spikes
OL,6,FLonger term, the war in Iran could
OL,7,Faffect demand, but he added: "If the
OL,8,Fconflict is, from a booking's
OL,9,Fperspective, like Ukraine or the Hamas
OL,10,Fattacks, what happened historically is
OL,11,Fthat bookings start to rise again
OL,12,Fafter about six weeks.
OL,14,F"So, right now, it's in line with what
OL,15,Fwe're expecting."
OL,26,@oD@^OUvD@AOUwD@QO]
