PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F427A1774523167
OL,3,CEasyJet boss warns fliers to book
OL,4,Cearly amid fuel price spikes
OL,6,FAsked for his message to the Prime
OL,7,FMinister about the ongoing war, he
OL,8,Fsaid: "What I would say, as CEO, is to
OL,9,Fmake sure that they think of aviation,
OL,10,Fand they think of the importance of
OL,11,Fthe economy of growth in aviation."
